    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "In the string template, you cannot set the `numberLocale`.\r\n\r\nThis is a wrapper over [`Number.prototype.toLocaleString()`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/toLocaleString). I thought we would expose all helpers in there.",
